Oh. you're a happily ever after guy.

17
00:01:47.723 --> 00:01:49.100
Yeah.

18
00:01:50.191 --> 00:01:51.968
Detective. what are you looking at?

19
00:01:52.093 --> 00:01:53.169
You just bought a ring.

20
00:01:53.294 --> 00:01:54.270
That's not what I'm looking at.

21
00:01:54.395 --> 00:01:55.438
Come on. don't ruin it for me.

22
00:01:55.563 --> 00:01:58.098
No. she wears Armani.
makes low six figures.

23
00:01:58.609 --> 00:01:59.485
drives a BMW. and is falling

24
