25
00:02:01.320 --> 00:02:02.945
Nothing but trouble. Hank.

26
00:02:03.070 --> 00:02:04.547
Why can't you just look
at her ass like the rest of us?

27
00:02:04.672 --> 00:02:06.015
- I can't.
- Come on. Nick.

28
00:02:06.140 --> 00:02:07.076
We have a call.

29
00:02:21.689 --> 00:02:23.433
The hiker flagged me down.

30
00:02:23.558 --> 00:02:25.151
He came through the ravine and said

31
00:02:25.276 --> 00:02:26.652
he saw something pretty bad.

32
00:02:26.777 --> 00:02:28.771
I didn't know
what he was talking about

33
00:02:28.896 --> 00:02:30.311
until he showed me this.

34
00:02:40.359 --> 00:02:42.403
The rest of her is off-trail.

35
00:02:49.493 --> 00:02:51.294
How do you know it's a her?

36
00:02:51.419 --> 00:02:52.789
Because of this.

37
00:02:54.672 --> 00:02:55.750
Woman's Nike.

38
00:02:55.916 --> 00:02:57.617
What kind of animal could do this?

39
00:02:57.742 --> 00:02:59.652
Normally. we'd be able
to tell by the tracks.

40
00:02:59.777 --> 00:03:01.130
a bear. cougar. wolf.

41
00:03:01.296 --> 00:03:02.522
Which one is it?

42
00:03:02.647 --> 00:03:04.424
Well. that's
where this gets interesting.

43
00:03:04.549 --> 00:03:06.893
This is the only track we found.

44
00:03:07.018 --> 00:03:08.795
Hey. we got a boot print down here.

45
00:03:08.920 --> 00:03:10.306
- We're gonna need a cast.
- Right away.

46
00:03:10.472 --> 00:03:15.394
DNA'll tell us
if this is your case or ours.

47
00:03:15.560 --> 00:03:16.736
