a month ago

48
00:03:16.861 --> 00:03:17.904
at Munson Creek Falls.

49
00:03:18.029 --> 00:03:19.655
Same deal.
Hiker and a bobcat.

50
00:03:19.780 --> 00:03:22.341
But the bobcat wasn't wearing boots.

51
00:03:22.466 --> 00:03:24.077
Do you hear something?

52
00:03:24.202 --> 00:03:26.913
- What?
- Music.

53
