55
00:03:34.045 --> 00:03:35.288
♪ Everybody's ♪

56
00:03:35.455 --> 00:03:37.356
Hank. we got an iPod over here.

57
00:03:37.481 --> 00:03:40.126
- What's this song?
- <i>Sweet Dreams.</i>

58
00:03:40.251 --> 00:03:41.694
Eurythmics.

59
00:03:41.819 --> 00:03:43.196
One of their better.

60
00:03:43.321 --> 00:03:45.064
♪ Sweet dreams are made of these ♪

61
00:03:45.189 --> 00:03:46.799
♪ Who am I to disagree? ♪

62
00:03:46.924 --> 00:03:48.468
